.SS ‚ò§ Code Style Checking
.sp
Pipenv has \fI\%Flake 8\fP built into it. You can check the style of your code like so, without installing anything:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
$ cat t.py
