.SS ‚ò§ Automatic Loading of \fB\&.env\fP
.sp
If a \fB\&.env\fP file is present in your project, \fB$ pipenv shell\fP and \fB$ pipenv run\fP will automatically load it, for you:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
$ cat .env
